sequenceDiagram
    participant PA as Project Architect
    participant OE as Orchestration Engine
    participant KR as Knowledge Repository
    participant AAR as AI Agent Runtime
    participant TIG as Tool Integration Gateway
    participant EE as Execution Engine
    participant GM as Governance Module

    PA->>OE: Submit documentation task instruction
    OE->>OE: Workflow Engine creates documentation workflow
    OE->>OE: Task Manager instantiates: Generate → Review → Validate
    OE->>AAR: Assign Generate task to Documentation Agent
    AAR->>KR: Read project context (read-only)
    KR-->>AAR: Foundation, Domain, UL, Project State
    AAR->>TIG: Invoke AI Provider for generation
    TIG-->>AAR: Generated document content
    AAR-->>OE: Draft document artifact produced

    OE->>AAR: Assign Review task to Review Agent
    AAR->>KR: Read draft + project standards + UL
    KR-->>AAR: Project knowledge context
    AAR->>TIG: Invoke AI Provider for review analysis
    TIG-->>AAR: Review analysis
    AAR-->>OE: Review report (quality, terminology, completeness)

    OE->>AAR: Assign Validate task to Validation Agent
    AAR->>KR: Read acceptance criteria
    KR-->>AAR: Task acceptance criteria
    AAR-->>OE: Validation result

    OE->>EE: Deliver artifact candidate + review + validation result
    EE->>EE: Artifact Producer assembles production-ready document
    EE->>EE: Validation Engine checks acceptance criteria
    EE->>GM: Submit for governance review

    GM->>GM: Documentation Standards Validator checks DDS compliance
    GM->>PA: Route to Approval Gate (human decision required)
    PA-->>GM: Approval decision

    alt Approved
        GM->>GM: Audit Logger records approval event
        GM->>KR: Store approved artifact in Documentation Store
        KR-->>PA: Artifact available in Knowledge Repository
    else Rejected
        GM->>OE: Rejection report
        OE->>PA: Rejection report delivered
    end
